      <title>高盛将黄金目标提高到3,100美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/goldman-raises-gold-target-to-3-100-on-central-bank-appetite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团公司（Goldman Sachs Group Inc.）将其年终的黄金目标提高到中央银行购买的每盎司3,100美元，并流入了以金银的交易所交易资金的流入，这强调了华尔街对金属的热情。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/goldman-raises-gold-target-to-3-100-on-central-bank-appetite</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 04:10:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
