      <title>三菱汽车在新闻本田上攀登，向更多日产汽车开放</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/mitsubishi-motors-climbs-on-news-honda-open-to-more-nissan-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三菱汽车公司的股价飙升了多达8.6％，是两个月以来最多的，这是在报告本田汽车公司愿意重新开始与生病的同行日产汽车公司进行潜在合作的报告。乌奇达往下走。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/mitsubishi-motors-climbs-on-news-honda-open-to-more-nissan-talks</guid>
